3. Usage
--------

Do this:

    $ mkdir "=build"
    $ cd "=build"

to inspect the available configuration options:

    $ ../configure --help

then do it:

    $ ../configure [options]
    $ make
    $ make test

  This package only compiles a set of test programs, it does
not produce things to install.


